{"tid":2066594,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉包圍深水埗警署多 14 人被控暴動　最細僅 14 歲　有被告投訴遭警棍毆 值日官:「唔好扮嘢」","createTime":"2020-06-16T11:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T01:26:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"035903cf48c1c1aff6fb75590ffc0e52551a59cd","tid":2066594,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:20:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%9A-14-%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%B0%E5%83%85-14-%E6%AD%B2-%E6%9C%89%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D%E6%AF%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25A4%259A-14-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E5%2583%2585-14-%25E6%25AD%25B2-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D%25E6%25AF%2586%2F&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=82a0dd19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25A4%259A-14-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E5%2583%2585-14-%25E6%25AD%25B2-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D%25E6%25AF%2586%2F&h=11f02165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%9A-14-%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%B0%E5%83%85-14-%E6%AD%B2-%E6%9C%89%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D%E6%AF%86/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年 8 月 29 日有示威者於深水埗警署外聚集，並被指投擲磚塊及以鐳射光線照射警署。警方在行動中拘捕了 18 人，年齡介乎 14 至 41 歲，當中 8 人為 18 歲以下。有 3 人去年已被警方以暴動罪起訴，其餘 15 人分別獲准保釋及「踢保」，警方上月再次拘捕他們及通緝一名在逃人士，罪名包括暴動罪及在公眾地方藏有攻擊性武器。<br />\n<br />\n代表第一被告的大律師郭憬憲在庭上投訴，有 5 至 6 名警員拘捕被告時用警棍打其頭部、膊頭及腰，把他完全制服後再以胡椒噴霧噴面。郭續指，被告稱雖然看不到，但感覺到有警員跪頸，他在警署曾向值日官要求驗傷，值日官卻說「唔好扮嘢」。"},{"pid":"05bd92d2f4e47ad124c44f9d2822b40fc160d805","tid":2066594,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:24:39.000Z","msg":"手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56ad40a4b66baddc19a9e6e3c1d0a30baf2232e","tid":2066594,"uid":168400,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76cd35b178f1bda086d2b0a66e0847f327c3fc3c","tid":2066594,"uid":263618,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"以鐳射光線照射警署<br />\n<br />\n咁又暴動"},{"pid":"682b65763f0351c3fb25bd2d90b920e0a5b2d29d","tid":2066594,"uid":60129,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"76cd35b178f1bda086d2b0a66e0847f327c3fc3c","tid":2066594,"uid":263618,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"以鐳射光線照射警署<br />\n<br />\n咁又暴動"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"想知暴動可以低門檻成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c8ffae25b0cca181986a1c46b53861dc9f75d9","tid":2066594,"uid":57205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"以後香港法例淨返暴動罪算啦"},{"pid":"2ac2c74bb8cf02ab89c3fc1270d59d408e0f336d","tid":2066594,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:56:31.000Z","msg":"黑警有特權"},{"pid":"34fbd5250bf41e9